metadata.name: Me!!
metadata.description:
This work is the culmination of my still short life in digital art, combining 11 of my works into one. It is also my first foundation piece!

Edition of 1

JPG,   5.8MP,    2117 x 2729,    3.0MB

Terms of use: The purchased NFT is a digital artwork that is uniquely identified in the blockchain and uploaded as an edition of 1. The buyer purchases a limited edition copy of the digital artwork to own. Upon purchase, the buyer may access the digital file to view or print on any digital device for personal use.
